Other recordings
Manzanero has sung Por Debajo de la Mesa as a duet Peruvian musician Tania Libertad on the duo's studio album Manzanero y la Libertad 1998 and with Chano Domnguez and Carmen Paris on Manazero's album Duetos 2 2002.cite web title=Manzanero y la Libertad&nbsp; Overview url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/manzanero-y-la-libertad-mw0000051683 accessdate=2014-01-03 work=Allmusic publisher=Rovi Corporationcite web title=Duetos 2&nbsp; Overview url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/duetos-2-mw0000663282 accessdate=2014-01-03 work=Allmusic publisher=Rovi Corporation He also performed the song in a concert with Argentine pianist Ral di Blasio in 1999 which was included on the latter's live album Bohemia, Vol.2 2000 and also performed the song live with fellow Mexican singer Susana Zabaleta on their album De la A a la Z 2006.cite web title=Bohemia, Vol. 2&nbsp; Overview url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/bohemia-vol-2-mw0000068860 accessdate=2014-01-03 work=Allmusic publisher=Rovi Corporationcite web title=De la A a la Z DVD&nbsp; Overview url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/de-la-a-a-la-z-dvd-mw0001222879 accessdate=2014-01-03 work=Allmusic publisher=Rovi Corporation

